    apply isS3
    all_goals try tauto
    all_goals try exact ‹T2Space M›
    all_goals try exact ‹ChartedSpace (EuclideanSpace ℝ (Fin 3)) M›
    all_goals try exact ‹SimplyConnectedSpace M›
    all_goals try exact ‹CompactSpace M›
